This directory contains the resources for running the RMI client/server system
used for accessing vegbank plots stored in MS ACCESS format database files.

STARTING THE SERVER
-------------------
1] extract the contents of the ./lib/rmiserver.tar file 
2] create the ODBC datasource that is to be used by the server application
    the default settings are 
    odbc_name: test_access; 
    location:C:\cygwin\tmp\rmi_exp.mdb

3] start the rmiregistry application
4] run the start_rmi_server.bat file 


REQUIRED JARS FILES
-------------------
utilities.jar -- the vegbank servlet utilities jar file, used for connecting to
the vegbank plantlookup servlet using HTTP.
planttaxonomy.jar -- contains classes for plant taxonomy purposes
jdbc7.0-1.2.jar -- the postgresql jdbc drivers.
database_access.jar -- the classes that allow connection to the main vegbank
  plots database

datatranslator.jar -- the classes used to transform the plot input data into a
  common data source 


OTHER REQUIREMENTS
------------------
./lib/ascii-treeview.xsl -- a generic xml-treeview stylesheet.
